                        <div id="page-title">
                            SCP-CN-963
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<span class="myTitle" style="display: none;">机械宇宙</span><span class="myClass" style="display: none;">Euclid</span><span class="myPreview" style="display: none;">机械隐藏在帷幕之前，齿轮啮合中宇宙演变。</span>


<div class="creditRate">
<div class="rateBox">
