<p>本文作者为<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meltyland-nightmare" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6167306); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6167306&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608342566" alt="Meltyland Nightmare" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6167306)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meltyland-nightmare" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6167306); return false;">Meltyland Nightmare</a></span>，该作者的更多作品见<a href="/erwin-schrodinger-s-personnel-files">首席研究员祖绫的人事页。</a><br />
<strong>本文配图信息：</strong><br />
安保模因配图为公共资源：<a href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Apophysis-100303-104.jpg#mw-jump-to-license">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Apophysis-100303-104.jpg#mw-jump-to-license</a></p>
</div>
